RUNNING LOCALLY (ADVANCED)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

If you want to run the app on your computer instead of Netlify, you MUST use a local server. Double-clicking the file (file:// protocol) will block all API calls.

1. Open Terminal (Mac) or PowerShell (Windows)
2. Navigate to your folder: cd path/to/folder
3. Start server: python3 -m http.server 8000
4. Open browser: http://localhost:8000/ipl-fantasy-v4_render.html


