PHASE 4 — FIRST TIME ADMIN SETUP
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Step 8 — Log in as admin

  Open your Netlify URL
  Click "Admin" on the login screen
  Enter PIN: 0000 (the default)

Step 9 — Change your admin PIN

  Go to League Setup tab
  In the Admin PIN field, replace 0000 with your own 4-digit PIN
  Click Save
  Remember this PIN — it's the only way back into the admin panel

Step 10 — Generate the join link

  Still in League Setup tab
  Click "Generate Join Link"
  You'll see a 6-character join code and a full URL
  Click Copy → send the link to your friends on WhatsApp


