PHASE 5 — GET CRICKETDATA.ORG API KEY
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Step 11 — Get your API key

  Go to cricketdata.org and sign up / log in
  Copy your API key from the dashboard
  This app uses a paid plan for full scorecard access

Step 12 — Save the API key in the app

  Admin panel → Current Match tab → API Key field
  Paste your key → click "Save Key"
  The app will use this for all live data fetches


