PHASE 7 — MEMBER FLOW (EACH MATCH)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  1. Open the league URL → enter name + PIN
  2. My Team tab → tap players to build your XI (max 6 from any one IPL team)
  3. Choose Captain (2×) and Vice-Captain (1.5×)
  4. Optionally apply a Booster from the booster dock (see Booster section below)
  5. Tap "LOCK IN MY TEAM"
  6. After admin clicks START MATCH → Match Info tab appears automatically
     showing the live batting/bowling scorecard (disappears when match ends)
  7. Live Scores tab for the leaderboard and pitch view
  8. Season Table tab for cumulative standings


