BOOSTER SYSTEM
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Each member gets a season inventory of boosters:

  Triple (3×)  — 2 per season — multiplies your entire match total by 3×
  Double (2×)  — 3 per season — multiplies your entire match total by 2×
  Team   (2×)  — 2 per season — multiplies all players from a chosen IPL
                                 team in your XI by 2×

Rules:
  - One booster per match. Can be changed or removed until you lock in.
  - League stage only — boosters are blocked for Qualifiers, Eliminators, Final.
  - Revealed at lock — type and target are visible to everyone the moment
    admin clicks START MATCH.
  - Booster stacks on top of Captain/VC multipliers.
  - If you already locked in your team and then apply/change a booster,
    it saves automatically — no need to re-lock.


