Step 18 — Keep your repository in sync

  If you make changes to your local file or update settings,
  use these commands to push them to GitHub:

  1.  Open your terminal/command prompt
  2.  Navigate to your project folder:
      cd path/to/IPL-FANTASY
  3.  Add your changes:
      git add .
  4.  Commit your changes:
      git commit -m "Update v3.6.8"
  5.  Push to GitHub:
      git push

  To get the latest updates from the main repo:
  1.  git pull
